    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anni ab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo nonagesimo tercio, pontificatus vero domini
                        nostri <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/4301">Clementis</persName> summi
                        pontificis et universalis pape in apostolica sacratissima beati Petri
                        apostoli Domini sede anno decimo, regnante domnus <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77">Enricus</persName> res in Italia
                        anno quintodecimo, die quarto intrante mense octuber, indictione prima, in
                        claustra qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3524">Cornedo</placeName>. <rs
                            key="#Breve/memoratorium">Breve recordacionis</rs> facio ego <persName
                            key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Martinus de Roncono"
                            >Martinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> de <placeName>Roncono</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> que est posita in <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Size #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Confinia #Feudum"
                            ref="#estates/2452">
                            <placeName key="#Size #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Confinia #Feudum"
                                >Matraria</placeName></geogName> quam dedit domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599">Geronimus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> pro <rs key="#Feudum">feudo</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes/Gastaldus"> Iohannis Castaldionis
                            </name></persName> vocatus, qui est abitator in <rs key="#Burgi"
                            >burgo</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Burgi" ref="#places/80">Ferrarie</placeName>, in loco qui
                        vocatur <placeName>Brusata</placeName> et filio suo, abeant et detineant
                        donec persevierint neque abbas neque monachus oferre presumat nisi victa
                        culpa da tua fidelibus ecclesie et si fecerit conponat <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >uncias auri duas</rs>; nec ipsi non abeant licenciam nec vendere nec
                        donare nisi ad meum dominium vel ad meos supcessores ad nullum placitum vel
                            <rs key="#Districtio">districtum</rs> nisi ad me vel meis supcessores;
                        et si fecerint, tunc liceat mihi introire et tenere <rs key="#Confinia"
                            >latera</rs> uius terre et sunt a duobus lateribus in <placeName
                            key="#Confinia">Vaginonum</placeName>, tercio latere <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >flumen</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers #Confinia" ref="#places/3546">Gabiane</placeName>,
                        in longo ubi alia terra tetenndi et <rs key="#Size">in latitudine est
                            perticas duodecim, pedibus treginta</rs>. Hieronimus abbas Pomposiensis
                        subscripsi. <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Hubertus Pomposianus"
                                >Ubertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> in hac brevi subscripsi.</ab>
                </div>
